h1_title: The Beguiling Chant of the Pagoda Realm
content: Further up the cell tunnel, you may notice a Snake-Head Mushroom glowing blue... that can't be right. Try to harvest it, and you'll uncover an extremely strong Fungiman enemy.
promot:
This is an excerpt from the file 'Pagoda_Realm_Walkthrough.md', within the main section titled 'The Beguiling Chant of the Pagoda Realm', specifically from the subsection 'Upper Pagoda (Level 3)'.
The content is as follows:
Further up the cell tunnel, you may notice a Snake-Head Mushroom glowing blue... that can't be right. Try to harvest it, and you'll uncover an extremely strong Fungiman enemy.
